data.description: Price Reduced! Elevate your lifestyle with this immaculate two-bedroom one-level condo located in a charming community of 14 homes! The entire space has been thoughtfully revitalized, with attention to every detail. Step inside and be greeted by stunning laminate flooring throughout adding a touch of sophistication and durability. The kitchen has been thoughtfully redesigned w/sleek quartz countertops & beautiful cabinets, providing both functionality & style.  The open-concept design creates a seamless flow that maximizes the available space, creating an airy & inviting atmosphere. Situated in a prime location near shopping, restaurants, medical facilities, & I-5, you'll have everything at your fingertips!
